node.text: My journey back to Namibia to help spread awareness, to get involved and educated. I want my kids to see and know Africa the way i did....where all Africa’s animals thrive. It’s up to us to make a change!

node.title: My journey back home to Namibia to help save the rhinos 🦏

node.text:
Are You #ForWildlifeRangers ?

Like the iconic wildlife they protect, rangers deserve to be backed by an explosion of voices. We must spread the word about these vital frontline conservation defenders and the nature that depends on them.

Together we can reach millions. We can raise awareness, and we can mobilize support. It all starts with you. 

Lend us your voice, and speak up for wildlife defenders. If we shout loud enough, together we will be heard. Join in with #ForWildlifeRangers

Please donate and your generosity will be matched by the Scheinberg Relief Fund:  https://wildliferangerchallenge.org/donate-usa/
